00:21:18.880 --> 00:21:20.560 line:20%
'Hari ini, aku bersamamu.'

00:21:21.640 --> 00:21:24.280 line:20%
"Dan tidak ada orang
ketiga di antara kita."

00:21:25.480 --> 00:21:27.440 line:20%
'Saya sangat mencintaimu.'

00:21:29.440 --> 00:21:31.360 line:20%
'Saya sangat mencintaimu.'

00:21:32.560 --> 00:21:34.160 line:20%
"Kau juga mencintaiku, kan?"

